#!/api/jslet.ui.DBControl' rel='jslet.ui.DBControl' class='docClass'>jslet.ui.DBControl</a><div class='subclass '><a href='#!/api/jslet.ui.AbstractDBTable' rel='jslet.ui.AbstractDBTable' class='docClass'>jslet.ui.AbstractDBTable</a><div class='subclass '><strong>jslet.ui.DBTable</strong></div></div></div></div><h4>Files</h4><div class='dependency'><a href='source/jslet.dbtable.html#jslet-ui-DBTable' target='_blank'>jslet.dbtable.js</a></div></pre><div class='doc-contents'><p>DBTable is a powerful control, features: <br /></p>\n\n<ol>\n<li>\n<dl><dt>Sort Data</dt><dd>Clicking column header text to sort data, SHIFT + Clicking column header text to sort data with multiple columns.</dd></dl>\n</li>\n<li>\n<dl><dt>Find Data</dt><dd>Pressing CTRL + F to pop up finding dialog.</dd></dl>\n</li>\n<li>\n<dl><dt>Filter Data</dt><dd>Pressing the down-arrow of each column header to pop up filtering dialog.</dd></dl>\n</li>\n<li>\n<dl><dt>Copy Data to Clipboard</dt><dd>First select cells(CTRL + A, CTRL/SHIFT + Clicking Cell), pressing CTRL + C to copy data.</dd></dl>\n</li>\n<li>\n<dl><dt>Find Error Record</dt><dd>When importing records or batch editing records, press CTRL + E to find the next record existing error.</dd></dl>\n</li>\n<li>\n<dl><dt>Multi-Layer Column Header</dt><dd>Set dataset field's property \"children\".</dd></dl>\n</li>\n<li>\n<dl><dt>Change Column Width</dt><dd>Drag and drop column line.</dd></dl>\n</li>\n<li>\n<dl><dt>Move Column</dt><dd>Drag and drop column header.</dd></dl>\n</li>\n<li>\n<dl><dt>Support Sequence Column</dt><dd>Set property \"hasSeqCol\" to true to show sequence column; <br />\nSet property \"reverseSeqCol\" to \"true\" to reverse sequence no; <br />\nSet property \"seqColHeader\" to customize sequence header. </dd></dl>\n</li>\n<li>\n<dl><dt>Support Select Column</dt>\n<dd>Set property \"hasSelectCol\" to \"true\" to show select column.<br />\nClicking \"Select Column\" header to select all records.<br />\nSet property \"selectBy\" to group select records.<br />\nSet dataset event \"onCheckSelectable\" to check which records can be selected. \n</dd></dl>\n</li>\n<li>\n<dl><dt>Support Action Column</dt><dd>Add a \"ACTION\" type field to dataset. </dd></dl>\n</li>\n<li>\n<dl><dt>Support Edit Action Column</dt><dd>Add a \"EDITACTION\" type field to dataset. </dd></dl>\n</li>\n<li>\n<dl><dt>Support Fixed rows or columns</dt><dd>Set value to properties \"fixedRows\" or \"fixedCols\". </dd></dl>\n</li>\n<li>\n<dl><dt>Support \"Total\" row</dt><dd>Set the dataset field's properties: \"aggregated\" and \"aggregatedBy\". </dd></dl>\n</li>\n<li>\n<dl><dt>Support Merge Rows with Same Value</dt><dd>Set the dataset field's properties: \"mergeSame\" and \"mergeSameBy\". </dd></dl>\n</li>\n<li>\n<dl><dt>Tree-Grid Style</dt><dd>Set property: \"treeField\". </dd></dl>\n</li>\n<li>\n<dl><dt>In-cell Edit</dt><dd>Set property: \"editable\" to true. </dd></dl>\n</li>\n<li>\n<dl><dt>Customize Table Style</dt><dd>Use: \"noborder\", \"onFillRow\", \"onFillCell\", \"hideHead\" to customize. </dd></dl>\n</li>\n<li>\n<dl><dt>Stretch Table Height Automatically</dt><dd>Use: \"autoStretch\", \"minVisibleRows\", \"onFillCell\", \"maxVisibleRows\" to customize. </dd></dl>\n</li>\n</ol>\n\n\n<p>Example:</p>\n\n<pre class='inline-example '><code>var jsletParam = {type:\"DBTable\", dataset: \"employee\"};\n\n//1. Declaring:\n&lt;div id=\"chartId\" data-jslet='type:\"DBTable\", dataset: \"employee\"' /&gt;\nor\n&lt;div data-jslet='jsletParam' /&gt;\n\n//2. Binding\n&lt;div id=\"ctrlId\"  /&gt;\n//Js snippet\nvar el = document.getElementById('ctrlId');\n<a href=\"#!/api/jslet.ui-method-bindControl\" rel=\"jslet.ui-method-bindControl\" class=\"docClass\">jslet.ui.bindControl</a>(el, jsletParam);\n\n//3. Create dynamically\n<a href=\"#!/api/jslet.ui-method-createControl\" rel=\"jslet.ui-method-createControl\" class=\"docClass\">jslet.ui.createControl</a>(jsletParam, document.body);\n</code></pre>\n</div><div class='members'><div class='members-section'><div class='definedBy'>Defined By</div><h3 class='members-title icon-property'>Properties</h3><div class='subsection'><div id='property-aggregated' class='member first-child inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><a href='#!/api/jslet.ui.AbstractDBTable' rel='jslet.ui.AbstractDBTable' class='defined-in docClass'>jslet.ui.AbstractDBTable</a><br/><a href='source/jslet.dbtable.html#jslet-ui-AbstractDBTable-property-aggregated' target='_blank' class='view-source'>view source</a></div><a href='#!/api/jslet.ui.AbstractDBTable-property-aggregated' class='name expandable'>aggregated</a> : Function<span class=\"signature\"></span></div><div class='description'><div class='short'>Identify the table has aggregated row or not. ...</div><div class='long'><p>Identify the table has aggregated row or not.</p>\n<h3 class=\"pa\">Parameters</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'>aggregated</span> : Boolean | undefined<div class='sub-desc'><p>True - the table has aggregated row, false(default) - otherwise.</p>\n</div></li></ul><h3 class='pa'>Returns</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'>this | Boolean</span><div class='sub-desc'>\n</div></li></ul></div></div></div><div id='property-autoClearSelection' class='member  inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><a href='#!/api/jslet.ui.AbstractDBTable' rel='jslet.ui.AbstractDBTable' class='defined-in docClass'>jslet.ui.AbstractDBTable</a><br/><a href='source/jslet.dbtable.html#jslet-ui-AbstractDBTable-property-autoClearSelection' target='_blank' class='view-source'>view source</a></div><a href='#!/api/jslet.ui.AbstractDBTable-property-autoClearSelection' class='name expandable'>autoClearSelection</a> : Function<span class=\"signature\"></span></div><div class='description'><div class='short'>Identify whether automatically clear selection when selecting table cells. ...</div><div class='long'><p>Identify whether